{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Save the world with breakbeats.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On the surface, he is a superhero. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But in his true form, he is an up-and-coming DJ who keeps the clubs lively night after night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">His name is BrebeMan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every day, he plays breakbeats from two records and defends the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of course, he never misses to proselytize breakbeat sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you finish this game, you will be hooked on breakbeats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the true music game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SYSTEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;BrebeMan&quot; is a 3D SHMUPS &amp; music game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You control the superhero \u201cBrebeMan\u201d and defeat the enemy \u201cKlangeist\u201d.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURING</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The disc manipulated by BrebeMan is an offensive and defensive tool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At times it is a blade that slices the enemy, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and at other times it is a shield that protects you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you accumulate tension, you can &quot;change the beat&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Change the Beat&quot; attacks all enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A powerful boss awaits you at the end of each stage. Face them with all your might.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The music features a wide variety of club music styles,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">from classic to trendy, with drum'n'bass as the mainstay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interactive sounds that progress according to the game enhance the game.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Starting with BrebeMan , various characters are represented in the collage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vintage, vaporwave, retro-futuristic,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and various other visuals invite you into an unknown world.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734102444","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349980/page.bg.jpg?t=1734102444","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349980/b2234828fb7986e79ca0a883bc4eaf67ecafbe8e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734102444","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349980/b2234828fb7986e79ca0a883bc4eaf67ecafbe8e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734102444","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Save the world with breakbeats.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On the surface, he is a superhero. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But in his true form, he is an up-and-coming DJ who keeps the clubs lively night after night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">His name is BrebeMan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every day, he plays breakbeats from two records and defends the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of course, he never misses to proselytize breakbeat sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you finish this game, you will be hooked on breakbeats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the true music game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SYSTEM</h2><p clas